{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/episode-pilot-satria-heroes-kai-youtube/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Lama Dinanti, Episode Pilot Satria Heroes Kai Tayang di Youtube","content":"\n<p>Satria Heroes Kai, karakter tokusatsu yang digadang-gadang\nsebagai lanjutan Satria Garuda Bima, akhirnya tayang juga. Setelah\nterkatung-katung selama satu tahun tanpa kepastian tayang, Satria Heroes Kai kini\nbisa disaksikan di Youtube dalam bentuk episode pilot.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55739\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/episode-pilot-satria-heroes-kai-youtube/attachment/01-satria-heroes-kai-pilot/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-satria-heroes-kai-pilot\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-satria-heroes-kai-pilot-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" alt=\"Furio dan Rin. Sumber: Satria Heroes\" class=\"wp-image-55739\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/01-satria-heroes-kai-pilot-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Furio dan Rin. Sumber: Satria Heroes</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Sang Satria Naga yang dulu menjadi cameo dalam film Satria\nHeroes Bima-X: Revenge of Darkness ini kini tampil dalam serial solonya\nsendiri. Identitas aslinya adalah Furio (Jefriadi Rifata), seorang fotografer\nyang bertualang bersama temannya, Rin (Frieska Anastasia JKT48) menjelajahi\nreruntuhan tua.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Di salah satu reruntuhan tersebut, mereka bertemu dengan sosok siluman Donga serta Master-nya. Master mengklaim Furio sebagai orang terpilih untuk mengalahkan Mamoun (antagonis film Revenge of Darkness) dan pengikutnya: Giran, Doran, dan Sheera.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/david-ross-marvel-gundala-toronto/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">David Ross, Ilustrator Kondang Marvel, Puji Gundala</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55740\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/episode-pilot-satria-heroes-kai-youtube/attachment/02-satria-heroes-kai-pilot/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-satria-heroes-kai-pilot\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-satria-heroes-kai-pilot-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" alt=\"Mamoun dan kaki tangannya. Sumber: Satria Heroes\" class=\"wp-image-55740\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/02-satria-heroes-kai-pilot-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Mamoun dan kaki tangannya. Sumber: Satria Heroes</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Saat pasukan dan monster Mamoun turun ke Bumi, Furio\nmenggunakan changer serta kartunya untuk berubah menjadi Satria Naga Kai.\nMenggunakan jurus-jurus andalannya, Satria Naga Kai siap bertarung untuk\nmelindungi Bumi dan ornag-orang yang ia cintai.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Satria Heroes Kai seyogiyanya tayang di awal tahun 2019 lalu di stasiun TV SCTV. Rencananya bakal ada 13 episode dengan durasi masing-masing 2 jam, dan proses shooting pun sudah berjalan sejak bulan Desember 2018 lalu. Sayang pada bulan Januari 2019, penayangan Satria Heroes Kai <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SatriaHeroesID/status/1090604740868591616\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">ditunda</a> tanpa kejelasan tanggal baru.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55741\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/episode-pilot-satria-heroes-kai-youtube/attachment/03-satria-heroes-kai-pilot/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-satria-heroes-kai-pilot\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-satria-heroes-kai-pilot-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg\" alt=\"Furio berubah menjadi Satria Naga Kai. Sumber: Satria Heroes\" class=\"wp-image-55741\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-satria-heroes-kai-pilot.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/03-satria-heroes-kai-pilot-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Furio berubah menjadi Satria Naga Kai. Sumber: Satria Heroes</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Munculnya Satria Heroes Kai di Youtube dalam durasi kurang dari 30 menit bisa jadi menunjukkan perubahan arah baru dari serial ciptaan Reino Barack ini. Jika fokus ke depannya adalah di webseries, mereka bisa bebas menuturkan kisah Furio tanpa harus terjegal regulasi penyiaran. Namun di saat bersamaan, Satria Heroes Kai juga melewatkan beberapa keuntungan finansial dari deal iklan televisi.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apapun jadinya nanti, apakah Satria Heroes Kai bakal tetap di Youtube atau cuma singgah sementara, semoga ini bukan pertama dan terakhir kalinya kita melihat aksi Furio di layar kaca. Kamu bisa menonton episode pilot Satria Heroes Kai di bawah ini.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4Jplk7He-Yo\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"8eee1c17-decd-57e7-8a71-5e9edfb5f95c"}}}